NIST SP 800-82r3                                        Guide to Operational Technology (OT) Security
September 2023

D.4.7. Healthcare and Public Health
   •   U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) – https://www.fda.gov
           o Digital Health Center of Excellence
   •   Department of Health and Human Services (HHS) – https://www.hhs.gov
           o Health Sector Cybersecurity Coordination Center (HC3)
   •   American Hospital Association (AHA) – https://www.aha.org/
           o AHA Preferred Cybersecurity Provider (APCP) Program
   •   National Institutes of Health (NIH) – https://www.nih.gov
           o NIH Information Technology Acquisition and Assessment Center (NITAAC)
   •   American Medical Association (AMA) – https://www.ama-assn.org

D.4.8. Nuclear Reactors, Materials, and Waste
   •   U.S. Nuclear Regulatory Commission (NRC) – https://www.nrc.gov
           o Office of Nuclear Security and Incident Response Cyber Security Branch (CSB)
   •   International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) – https://www.iaea.org
   •   Nuclear Energy Agency (NEA) – https://www.oecd-nea.org
           o Digital Instrumentation and Control Working Group (DICWG)
   •   Nuclear Energy Institute (NEI) – https://www.nei.org
   •   World Institute of Nuclear Security (WINS) – https://www.wins.org

D.4.9. Transportation Systems
   •   U.S. Department of Transportation (DOT) – https://www.transportation.gov
           o Intelligent Transportation Systems Joint Program Office
   •   Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) – https://www.faa.gov
           o Aviation Cyber Initiative (ACI)
           o Air Traffic Organization (ATO) Cybersecurity Group
   •   Federal Highway Administration (FHWA) – https://highways.dot.gov
           o FHWA Office of Operations Research, Development, and Technology
   •   Federal Motor Carrier Safety Administration (FMCSA) – https://www.fmcsa.dot.gov
   •   Federal Railroad Administration (FRA) – https://railroads.dot.gov
           o FRA Office of Research, Development, and Technology
   •   Federal Transit Administration (FTA) – https://www.transit.dot.gov


